.SH "NAME"
smb_prometheus_endpoint \- Make Samba profiling information available to prometheus\&.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'\ 'u
smb_prometheus_endpoint [\-a\ ADDRESS] [\-p\ PORT] [smbprofile\&.tdb]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
This tool is part of the
\fBsamba\fR(8)
suite\&.
.PP
Make the Samba profiling information available to prometheus via http\&.
.SH "OPTIONS"
.PP
\-a ADDRESS
.RS 4
The address which
smb_prometheus_endpoint
shall listen on, default is 127\&.0\&.0\&.1\&.
.RE
.PP
\-p PORT
.RS 4
The port which
smb_prometheus_endpoint
shall listen on, default is port 9922\&.
.RE
.PP
smbprofile\&.tdb
.RS 4
The full path to the system\*(Aqs smbprofile\&.tdb where Samba stores its statistics\&.
.RE
.SH "AUTHOR"
.PP
The original Samba software and related utilities were created by Andrew Tridgell\&. Samba is now developed by the Samba Team as an Open Source project similar to the way the Linux kernel is developed\&.
